          "type": "text",
          "text": "gdGap",
          "annotations": {
            "code": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " directive. Each area is defined with ",
          "annotations": {}
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "gdArea",
          "annotations": {
            "code": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " directive.",
          "annotations": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "It‚Äôs notable that Grid directives also support the responsive enhancement as well as Flexbox! For example, the following template changes the card layout to a vertical column only in a narrow viewport. Updates are only two lines!",
          "annotations": {}
        }
      ]
